  | .

h3.mb-3.mt-4 Social Media Widgets

p Our web properties include several social media features, such as Facebook’s Like and Share buttons and other interactive programs hosted by social media sites. These features may collect your IP address, site activity, and often will require authentication and/or your social media credentials to function properly Op4G does not record or store this data, and any data submitted to a social media account will be governed by that site or company’s privacy policy.

h3.mb-3.mt-4 No Surprises

p Opinions4Good promises to post any changes to our privacy or other policies that affect member data on our website at least 7 days before making any change. If Opinions4Good intends to have a change in ownership or controlling interest, or if we make any material changes, members will be notified by email (sent to the e-mail address specified in your account) or by means of a notice on this site prior to any change.

